      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make sure the paper addresses the counter-arguments so it doesn't seem one-sided. people usually bring up the idea of meritocracy—like that people should just keep what they earn based on their hard work. how should i frame that viewpoint in my essay so it doesn't weaken my main argument about redistribution?",
